comments: Lopez (WAS) sets the screen on Murray (DEN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Murray (DEN) moves along Beal's (WAS) path and absorbs contact to his arm during the shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) sets the screen on Beal (WAS) and does not deliver contact.
Lopez (WAS) is established in Murray's (DEN) path and makes marginal contact with him after the screen.
Hachimura (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Jokic (DEN).
Porter Jr. (DEN) kicks his leg out unnaturally during his shot attempt and makes contact with Beal that affects his ability to defend.
Harris (DEN) makes marginal contact with Beal (WAS) during the drive.
Green (DEN) gets to ball height and cleanly blocks Beal's (WAS) shot attempt.
Hachimura (WAS) sets the screen on Murray (DEN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Lopez (WAS) sets the screen on Campazzo (DEN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Green (DEN) makes contact to Bertans' (WAS) arm and affects his ability to follow through naturally on his jump shot attempt.
Westbrook (WAS) grabs Jokic (DEN) and dislodges him from his position.
Hachimura (WAS) legally contests Murray's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Lopez (WAS) extends into Campazzo's (DEN) path while setting the screen and does not give him room to avoid the contact.
Campazzo (DEN) and Beal (WAS) briefly engage and separate at the start of the inbound.
Green (DEN) turns into Beal (WAS) and initiates contact that affects his shot attempt at the basket.
